angelo gordon  co  specialists in nontraditional investments why alternatives our expertise ag® strategies the team login home angelo gordon creativity experience angelo gordon  co is a privatelyheld registered investment advisor dedicated to alternative investing the firm was founded in  and currently manages approximately  billion we seek to generate absolute returns with low volatility by exploiting inefficiencies in selected markets and capitalizing on situations that are not in the mainstream of investment opportunities we creatively seek out new opportunities that allow us to remain a leader in alternative investments we have expertise in a broad range of absolute return strategies for both institutional and high net worth investors our dedicated team of employees seeks to deliver consistent positive returns in all market environments we have built our name on our breadth of talent intensive research and riskaverse approach to investing our longterm experience gives us the insight and patience to turn our vision into profitable stable businesses take a visual tour of angelo gordon ag® strategies credit distressed debt non investment grade corporate credit residential  consumer debt energy lending middle market direct lending real estate real estate private equity real estate debt net lease real estate private equity private equity multi strategy convertible arbitrage risk arbitrage multistrategy contact us questions comments send us an email media inquiries gasthalter  cotel   human resources in memoriam john m angelo june    january    angelo gordon  co  terms of use angelo gordon  co  specialists in nontraditional investments why alternatives our expertise ag® strategies the team login home  the team the team angelo gordon including affiliates has over  employees including more than  investment professionals many of our key professionals have worked together for more than a decade our reputation has helped us to attract and retain the highestcaliber employees many of whom are principals in the firm the firm has fullystaffed risk management accounting compliance and client service groups our research analysts specialize in a number of different but related investment strategies we encourage communication among all analysts in an effort to meet the common goal of understanding the risks and rewards of each investment opportunity we believe our greatest asset is the collaborative way in which the various disciplines work together management investor relations strategies corporate ag® strategies credit distressed debt non investment grade corporate credit residential  consumer debt energy lending middle market direct lending real estate real estate private equity real estate debt net lease real estate private equity private equity multi strategy convertible arbitrage risk arbitrage multistrategy snapshots of ag® a visual tour of angelo gordon contact us questions comments send us an email media inquiries gasthalter  cotel   human resources  angelo gordon  co  terms of use angelo gordon  co  specialists in nontraditional investments why alternatives our expertise ag® strategies the team login home  account login account login the following section of our web site contains proprietary information to gain access a username and password is required user name user name is required password password is required remember me    cant sign in click here if you do not currently have a usernamepassword or if you have any questions regarding this information please contact us i forgot my password if you need assistance please contact us email phone    password reset please enter your email address  email is required ag® strategies credit distressed debt non investment grade corporate credit residential  consumer debt energy lending middle market direct lending real estate real estate private equity real estate debt net lease real estate private equity private equity multi strategy convertible arbitrage risk arbitrage multistrategy snap