quity real estate strategies overview angelo gordon began investing in commercial real estate in  and has acquired over  billion of properties the firm focuses on a valueadded approach through the acquisition of subperforming real estate properties across a broad range of geographical markets and product types these assets are often attractively priced due to the lack of operating income complexity of analysis and inefficiency of the sales process with real estate professionals in our offices in new york los angeles london amsterdam frankfurt hong kong seoul and tokyo we have a global view of the market with a strong emphasis on the united states and asia we manage real estate assets in two distinct disciplines our opportunistic real estate strategy focuses on properties where a great deal of repositioning and renovation is usually required to stabilize the asset and which target a higher rate of return than our more conservative core plus real estate strategy our core plus real estate strategy focuses on higher quality assets which despite their subperformance generate significant current income from operations generally we will work in tandem with one of many local operating partners to source real estate deals and correct the assets underperformance our real estate teams experience encompasses all aspects of real estate investment and management including acquisition financing disposition leasing and construction management our real estate investment professionals have handson operational real estate expertise that has proved to be critical to our success in acquiring and repositioning assets real estate private equity senior professionals view representative case studies ag® strategies credit distressed debt non investment grade corporate credit residential  consumer debt energy lending middle market direct lending real estate real estate private equity real estate debt net lease real estate private equity private equity multi strategy convertible arbitrage risk arbitrage multistrategy snapshots of ag® a visual tour of angelo gordon contact us questions comments send us an email media inquiries gasthalter  cotel   human resources  angelo gordon  co  terms of use angelo gordon  co  specialists in nontraditional investments why alternatives our expertise ag® strategies the team login home  ag® strategies  private equity private equity private equity strategies about us angelo gordons private equity group manages over  billion in existing investments and committed capital we focus on acquiring businesses and assets with strong management that have the potential for meaningful growth and value creation why work with us large firm resources for smaller and middle market transactions we bring substantial resources a broad network of relationships and a wide range of experience to add value to our portfolio companies strong and deep relationships with financial partners lenders equity coinvestors etc and transaction advisors legal financial operational etc focused approach with experienced personnel our team of veteran investment professionals and seasoned senior advisors has the ability to identify transactions where we can uniquely add value key relationships with senior advisors include public company ceos industry veterans experienced investors managementcentric approach we recognize that we are not operators accordingly we seek to partner with world class management teams as value added contributors our mission is to complement the skill sets of our management teams with i angelo gordon resources ii senior advisor experience and iii investment professional financial acumen we offer our management partners compelling equity incentive programs unlike the vast majority of our peers we do not charge portfolio management or transaction fees proven track record of success our focused approach and broad experience within our key industries has produced strong and quantifiable results our investment professionals have a long and distinguished track record within our core verticals we seek to generate returns through fundamental growth rather than financial engineering about private equity investment criteria portfolio private equity news our team ag® strategies credit distressed debt non investment grade corporate credit residential  consumer debt energy lending middle market direct lending real estate real estate private equity real estate debt net lease real estate private equity private equity multi strategy convertible arbitrage risk arbitrage multistrategy snapshots of ag® a visual tour of angelo gordon contact us questions comments send us an email media inquiries gasthalter  cotel   human resources  angelo gordon  co  terms of use angelo gordon  co  specialists in nontraditional investments why alternatives our expertise ag® strategies the team login home  our expertise consistent absolute returns identifying opportunities there are periods when a market sector or security becomes mispriced because investors do not recognize its true value or do not have the platform or network to access the opportunity these periods may be long or shortlived but in either case an investor can benefit from these inefficiencies  angelo gordon has a long history of identifying and successfully exploiting mispricings in securities and assets through rigorous and extensive analysis of company and industry fundamentals research is the cornerstone of angelo gordon’s investment process our firm has more than  investment professionals working together over the years we have built an extensive network of relationships which provides us with substantial deal flow we are in an excellent position to capitalize on the best investment ideas at any time protecting capital our focus on fundamental research is complemented by strict adherence to our disciplined style — focus on the downside diversify and use leverage judiciously  our philosophy is that by understanding the potential downside or loss of an investment and sizing our positions accordingly we will be able to generate aboveaverage returns with low volatility over a long period of time managing risk in addition to the risk management techniques employed by the portfolio managers of each strategy fundamental research diversification etc the firm has an independent risk management group which analyzes the exposures and activities within portfolios the risk management team takes an integrated approach to analyze market credit and operational risk across all of angelo gordon’s portfolios  angelo gordon’s chief risk officer and staff maintain a comprehensive risk management framework which includes welldefined policies through bottomup analysis daily portfolio monitoring and regular evaluation of capital adequacy and performance forecasts the risk management group operates independently to ensure that all activities in the firm are performed in a fair and transparent manner  the risk management group is responsible for reviewing all systems products and pricing models the group also reviews the weekly price variance reports the weekly and quarterly fair market valuations quarterly best execution reports and performs counterparty credit analysis for all brokers the chief risk officer also ensures that the antimoney launderingofac reviews are performed and chairs the brokerage valuation and disaster recoverybusiness continuity committees investment process angelo gordon has significant analytical experience in both equity and debt markets in addition we have internal industry specialists and outside partners with expertise in specific fields we use this wealth of internal and external resources to come up with ideas and analyze investment opportunities that generate attractive riskadjusted returns we have an excellent track record of over  years of investing across a broad range of alternative investment strategies  michael l gordon ag® strategies credit distressed debt non investment grade corporate credit residential  consumer debt energy lending middle market direct lending real estate real estate private equity real estate debt net lease real estate private equity private equity multi strategy convertible arbitrage risk arbitrage multistrategy snapshots of ag® a visual tour of angelo gordon contact us questions comments send us an email media inquiries gasthalter  cotel   human resources  angelo gordon  co  terms of use angelo gordon  co  wikipedia angelo gordon  co from wikipedia the free encyclopedia jump to navigation search angelo gordon  co type private industry alternative investment management products  distressed securities hedge funds leveraged buyouts founded   years ago  headquarters  park avenue new york city new york us total assets  billion  website wwwangelogordoncom angelo gordon  company is an american alternative investment manager founded in november  by john m angelo and michael l gordon who together ran the arbitrage department of lf rothschild in the s the firm is  employeeowned secregistered and has nearly  employees and more than  investment professionals angelo gordon focuses on four main investment disciplines credit real estate private equity and multistrategy within those broad categories the firm offers products in distressed debt and noninvestment grade corporate credit convertible and merger arbitrage residential and consumer debt energy direct lending real estate private equity real estate debt and lending net lease real estate private equity multistrategy and middle market direct lending angelo gordon offers two types of investment structures openended hedge fund products and closedended private equitystyle products the firm is headquartered in new york city with additional offices worldwide including in san francisco los angeles chicago houston london amsterdam hong kong seoul frankfurt and tokyo contents  history  management committee  awards and recognition  investments  references  external links  additional references historyedit john angelo and michael gordon founded the firm on strategies with which they had  years prior experience distressed securities risk arbitrage and convertible arbitrage the multistrategy platform was added in  as a way to offer investors a single fund which captured many of angelo gordon’s investment strategies and which could tactically allocate as markets shifted in  the leveraged loan business was added as an extension of the distressed debt business the firm began buying real estate as early as  through investments in the distressed debt of bankrupt real estate companies in  as real estate markets buckled under the weight of too much debt the firm launched its opportunistic real estate strategy investments with the goal of improving and repositioning the property by increasing operating income in early  the company added core plus real estate to its real estate strategies as it was able to benefit from its operating partner network and purchase high quality real estate since  the firm has expanded its real estate offerings through a dedicated opportunistic asian real estate strategy in the wake of the global financial crisis of  and the european banking crisis of  angelo gordon added european real estate to its strategies as prices were depressed and liquidity was severely curtailed in the region net lease real estate strategy was established in  to focus on below investment grade tenants angelo gordon further expanded into the intersections of real estate and credit with the addition of real estate debt in  and residential and consumer debt in  in  angelo gordon was one of only nine private investment firms to partner with the us department of the treasury the board of governors of the federal reserve system and the federal deposit insurance corporation in ppip—the privatepublic investment partnership the us government invested alongside the selected firms to unlock the frozen credit markets in the wake of the global financial crisis this was a successful program the firm took advantage of the post financial crisis contraction in bank lending to smaller companies through senior secure direct lending to energy companies in  and to middle market borrowers in the private equity sponsor community in  in october  larry schloss became the president of angelo gordon and co in march  mr schloss left the firm cofounder john m angelo died in  management committeeedit mr michael l gordon cofounder ceo and chief investment officer cio mr kirk wickman chief operating officer  mr josh baumgarten deputy cio and coportfolio manager multistrategy mr adam schwartz head of us  europe real estate  awards and recognitionedit angelo gordon’s portfolio managers have in recent years been noted for top performance in their investment strategies angelo gordon’s cmbs fund and the noninvestment grade corporate credit fund were recognized by bloomberg for best performance for directional fixed income   the rmbsabs fund appeared in barron’s top  hedge funds in  and in  angelo gordon’s flagship multistrategy fund appeared in business insider’s  most successful hedge funds in  bloomberg ‘s  top performing large hedge funds in  and won the award for creditflux best credit multistrategy in  investmentsedit angelo gordon operates three basic types of investment vehicles illiquid strategies — include a variety of investment strategies distressed securities private equity triple net lease and real estate liquid strategies — credit opportunities convertible arbitrage and risk arbitrage multistrategy — takes advantage of attractive alternative investment opportunities from a range of the firms disciplines referencesedit  murray sean  july  deal alert angelo gordon acquires reliant funding debanked retrieved  september    company profile for angelo gordon  co lp bloomberg retrieved  june    a b c d profile ipe retrieved  january  permanent dead link  a b c d e f company overview of angelo gordon  co bloomberg businessweek retrieved  january    angelo gordon  co wallstreetoasis